        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nopenstack parameter will be replaced by helm.\nall openstack parameter will be configured inside values.yaml.\n\nall urls inside mso-docker.json was hard coded so i changed to .Values.nsPrefix.\n\nExample:\n    \"mso-sdnc-adapter-config\":\n    {\n      \"sdncurls\":\n      [\n        \"http://sdnhost.onap-sdnc.svc.cluster.local:8282/restconf/operations/L3SDN-API:\",\n\nwill become\n\n    \"mso-sdnc-adapter-config\":\n    {\n      \"sdncurls\":\n      [\n        \"http://sdnhost.{{ .Values.nsPrefix }}-sdnc.svc.cluster.local:8282/restconf/operations/L3SDN-API:\",",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
